    <section_number>6</section_number>
    <catch_line>Representation By Attorney; Waiver</catch_line>
    <order_by>6</order_by>
    <text>
        A party shall have the right to be represented by an attorney at any proceeding or hearing under this chapter, notwithstanding any waiver of such right prior to the proceeding or hearing.
    </text>
